# Expense Tracker

A full-stack Expense Tracker built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript and Supabase.

## Features

- Add Expense
- Delete Expense
- Budget Tracker
- Remaining Budget
- Progress Bar
- Search Expenses
- Category Filter
- Sort Expenses
- Expense Date Tracking
- Monthly Report
- Last 7 Days Report
- CSV Download
- Pie Chart Analytics
- Supabase Database Integration

## Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Supabase
- Chart.js
- GitHub Pages

